#: .\ammo.json .\ammo_types.json
msgid "550 Arlov"
msgid_plural "550 Arlovs"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': '550 Arlov'}
#: .\ammo.json
msgid ""
"unique bullet for Vitrovski V-85 sniper rifle, it looks like .50 BMG but "
"much more slim and stronger."
msgstr ""

#: .\ammo.json
msgid "550 Arlov Incendiary"
msgid_plural "550 Arlov Incendiarys"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': '550 Arlov Incendiary'}
#: .\ammo.json
msgid ""
"Incendiary variant of 550 Arlov, this one has red tip that explode and "
"burning target on hit."
msgstr ""

#: .\ammo.json
msgid "550 Arlov AP"
msgid_plural "550 Arlov APs"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': '550 Arlov AP'}
#: .\ammo.json
msgid ""
"Variant of 550 Arlov that uses reinforced material to increase penetration "
"ability at cost of damage reduction."
msgstr ""

#: .\ammo.json
msgid "550 Arlov Explosive"
msgid_plural "550 Arlov Explosives"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': '550 Arlov Explosive'}
#: .\ammo.json
msgid ""
"Variant of 550 Arlov that uses explosive tip, a bit overkill for killing "
"zombies but enough to give damage to hard targets."
msgstr ""

#: .\ammo.json .\ammo_types.json
msgid "20mm Vulcan"
msgid_plural "20mm Vulcans"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': '20mm Vulcan'}
#: .\ammo.json
msgid ""
"bigger than .50 BMG, this 20mm bullet packs a powerful punch against "
"everything. and maybe an overkill for killing some undeads and humans."
msgstr ""

#: .\ammo.json .\ammo_types.json
msgid "9x39mm"
msgid_plural "9x39mms"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': '9x39mm'}
#: .\ammo.json
msgid ""
"Soviet rifle cartridge designed for good armor penetration and power, almost"
" similar to 7.62 used by AK-47, this one is unique for VSS Vintorez."
msgstr ""

#: .\ammo.json .\ammo_types.json
msgid "Cannon Ball"
msgid_plural "Cannon Balls"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cannon Ball'}
#: .\ammo.json
msgid ""
"huge ball of steel, specially designed to be fired from cannon of a boat or "
"portable cannon. you can imagine crushing some zombies with this."
msgstr ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid "XS-500"
msgid_plural "XS-500s"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid ""
"Powerful handcannon with built-in red dot sight and unique firing mechanism,"
" capable of delivering great damage for long-range target."
msgstr ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid "Vitrovski V-85"
msgid_plural "Vitrovski V-85s"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid ""
"Russian's manufactured sniper rifle capable of piercing a thick steel wall "
"thanks to its unique 550 Arlov bullet, it also has built-in muzzle brake and"
" rifle scope."
msgstr ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid "Eliminator"
msgid_plural "Eliminators"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid ""
"Highly-classified, futuristic laser cannon made by US government. meant for "
"last resort against the Cataclysm, seeing this weapon makes you believe they"
" never had a chance to use it properly."
msgstr ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid "VA-989"
msgid_plural "VA-989s"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid ""
"Before Cataclysm happened, a lot of elite military uses this laser rifle as "
"their main weapon, due to efficient energy consumption and deadly power. but"
" now it becomes scavenger's best friend in times of danger."
msgstr ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid "semi-auto"
msgstr ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid "3-shot"
msgstr ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid "Extrella XS-3"
msgid_plural "Extrella XS-3s"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid ""
"Made by Extrella Company, this handgun is famous for its firing mechanism "
"that result in almost no recoil and perfect accuracy. it also has built-in "
"scope for ease in aiming "
msgstr ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid "Anzio 20mm"
msgid_plural "Anzio 20mms"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid ""
"Designed by Anzio Ironworks, this large anti-material rifle uses 20mm Vulcan"
" bullet, delivering destructive power to anything it shoots, has built-in "
"scope and muzzle brake."
msgstr ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid "Pancor Jackhammer"
msgid_plural "Pancor Jackhammers"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid ""
"Designed by Pancor Corporation, this 12-gauge, blow-forward, gas-operated "
"bullpup automatic shotgun is what weapon's collector is looking before "
"Cataclysm. And only few of this exist in the world so you're on high luck if"
" you find this weapon."
msgstr ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid "semi auto"
msgstr ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid "auto"
msgstr ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid "Mk-1 Arm Gun"
msgid_plural "Mk-1 Arm Guns"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid ""
"Prototype Arm-mounted gun, chambered in 9mm and uses muscle sensor as "
"trigger, this weapon is designed by somebody who thinks why punch zombies "
"when you can shoot a bullet from your arm."
msgstr ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid "VSS Vintorez"
msgid_plural "VSS Vintorezs"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid ""
"Russian's special sniper rifle. uses Subsonic 9x39mm bullet and has built-in"
" scope and suppresor, this weapon is specially designed for undercover or "
"clandestine operation, or picking zombies silently."
msgstr ""

#: .\gun.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "rifle"
msgstr ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid "Portable Cannon"
msgid_plural "Portable Cannons"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid ""
"Designed and produced by former pirate, this weapon almost looks like "
"pirate's boat cannon although its smaller and enough to be carried like "
"normal weapons. heavy, but has enough power to deliver a big oof to "
"everything thanks to its special cannonball bullet."
msgstr ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid "Winchester Liberator"
msgid_plural "Winchester Liberators"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid ""
"Made by Winchester Company, this 4-barrel prototype shotgun was failed "
"attempt at making cheap but effective shotgun. but somehow resurfaced and "
"become military choice sometimes before Cataclysm."
msgstr ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid "MTs255"
msgid_plural "MTs255s"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\gun.json
msgid ""
"Russian-made shotgun with 5-shell internal revolving cylinder, combining "
"revolver mechanism with shotgun apparently is a good combo for russians. it "
"also has picattiny rail for sight device."
msgstr ""

